# API service layer — abstracts all HTTP calls from components (SOLID: D)
# One file per resource. Components import services, never fetch() directly.
# Examples:
#   products.ts  — getProducts(), getProductById(), getProductsByCategory()
#   orders.ts    — createOrder(), getOrderById(), listUserOrders()
#   auth.ts      — login(), register(), logout(), getSession()
#   user.ts      — getUserProfile(), updateProfile()
